methods.name: public int getAdEventType()
methods.comment:
* Gets the {@link FrequencyCapFilters.AdEventType} for the ad counter histogram override. * *

The ad event type is used with the ad counter key from {@link #getAdCounterKey()} and the * buyer adtech from {@link #getBuyer()} to specify which histogram to use in ad selection * filtering. The ad event type would normally be specified by an app/SDK after a * FLEDGE-selected ad is rendered.

methods.name: public int getAdCounterKey()
methods.comment:
* Gets the ad counter key for the ad counter histogram override. * *

The ad counter key is used with the ad event type from {@link #getAdEventType()} and the * buyer adtech from {@link #getBuyer()} to specify which histogram to use in ad selection * filtering. The ad counter key would normally be specified by a custom audience ad to * represent a grouping to filter on.

methods.name: public AdTechIdentifier getBuyer()
methods.comment:
* Gets the {@link AdTechIdentifier} for the buyer which owns the ad counter histogram. * *

During filtering in FLEDGE ad selection, ads can only use ad counter histogram data * generated by the same buyer. For {@link FrequencyCapFilters#AD_EVENT_TYPE_WIN}, ad counter * histogram data is further restricted to ads from the same custom audience, which is * identified by the buyer, the custom audience's owner app package name, and the custom * audience name.
